{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/blog/2017/best-practices-for-push-notifications","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>As the web is moving forward very fast and now we can do almost everything on the web which can be done in native applications (<code class=\"language-text\">android</code> &#x26; <code class=\"language-text\">iOS</code>). Such as <code class=\"language-text\">offline contents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">push notifications</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">background sync</code> etc.</p>\n<p>But many websites started using these features in a bad way and only a few sites are using it in better ways to engage users.</p>\n<p>In this post, I will explain <code class=\"language-text\">why</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">when</code> you <code class=\"language-text\">should</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">shouldn&#39;t</code> prompt for push notifications.</p>\n<h3 id=\"good--bad-timing-for-asking-permission\" style=\"position:relative;\">Good &#x26; Bad timing for asking permission<a href=\"#good--bad-timing-for-asking-permission\" aria-label=\"good  bad timing for asking permission permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<h3 id=\"bad\" style=\"position:relative;\">Bad<a href=\"#bad\" aria-label=\"bad permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Asking for permission on the <code class=\"language-text\">first visit</code> (this pattern is repeated in most of the sites)</li>\n</ul>\n<center class=\"b\"><i>jabong.com</i></center>\n<center> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/4b39a/jabong.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.42857142857142%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Jabong Website\" title=\"Jabong Website\" src=\"/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/8c557/jabong.png\" srcset=\"/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/4edbd/jabong.png 175w,\n/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/13ae7/jabong.png 350w,\n/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/8c557/jabong.png 700w,\n/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/e996b/jabong.png 1050w,\n/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/2cefc/jabong.png 1400w,\n/static/7e7066d7dc76876bf2d14800ed1195d3/4b39a/jabong.png 3104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></center>\n<h3 id=\"good\" style=\"position:relative;\">Good<a href=\"#good\" aria-label=\"good permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ask for permission when it is <code class=\"language-text\">relevant</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Example:</h4>\n<p>After ordering something, prompt the user that you will give order status using push notifications.</p>\n<center class=\"b\"><i>Flipkart Website</i></center>\n<center> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/4b39a/flipkart.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.42857142857142%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Flipkart Website\" title=\"Flipkart Website\" src=\"/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/8c557/flipkart.png\" srcset=\"/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/4edbd/flipkart.png 175w,\n/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/13ae7/flipkart.png 350w,\n/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/8c557/flipkart.png 700w,\n/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/e996b/flipkart.png 1050w,\n/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/2cefc/flipkart.png 1400w,\n/static/a8458a06dec1a7e33396b2dacd682ca2/4b39a/flipkart.png 3104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></center>\n<h3 id=\"bad-1\" style=\"position:relative;\">Bad<a href=\"#bad-1\" aria-label=\"bad 1 permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Showing push notification <code class=\"language-text\">permission prompt</code> on every page load.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"good-1\" style=\"position:relative;\">Good<a href=\"#good-1\" aria-label=\"good 1 permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Show an option to <code class=\"language-text\">enable</code> push notification for certain categories. Let the user decide whether he/she wants the push notifications.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Example:</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://events.google.com/io/attending/\" target=\"_blank\">Google I/O 2017</a> site has options to enable for <code class=\"language-text\">attendees i/o notifications</code>.</p>\n<center class=\"b\"><i>Google I/O 2017 site</i></center>\n<center> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/a878e/push1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Google IO 2017 - Mobile\" title=\"Google IO 2017 - Mobile\" src=\"/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/8c557/push1.png\" srcset=\"/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/4edbd/push1.png 175w,\n/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/13ae7/push1.png 350w,\n/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/8c557/push1.png 700w,\n/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/e996b/push1.png 1050w,\n/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/2cefc/push1.png 1400w,\n/static/86fcdc834ff0b7c42542e2b84beca07d/a878e/push1.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></center>\n<h3 id=\"bad-2\" style=\"position:relative;\">Bad<a href=\"#bad-2\" aria-label=\"bad 2 permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>No option to <code class=\"language-text\">disable</code> the enabled push notifications.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"good-2\" style=\"position:relative;\">Good<a href=\"#good-2\" aria-label=\"good 2 permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Give the power to the user to <code class=\"language-text\">disable</code> notifications, so he/she can disable it when no longer needs it.</li>\n</ul>\n<center class=\"b\"><i>Google I/O 2017 site</i></center>\n<center> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/a878e/push2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Google IO 2017 - Mobile\" title=\"Google IO 2017 - Mobile\" src=\"/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/8c557/push2.png\" srcset=\"/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/4edbd/push2.png 175w,\n/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/13ae7/push2.png 350w,\n/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/8c557/push2.png 700w,\n/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/e996b/push2.png 1050w,\n/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/2cefc/push2.png 1400w,\n/static/3b6d401b1445a99f79e1eaae1eac7a02/a878e/push2.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></center>\n<h4>Browser Support</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Chrome</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Opera</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Mozilla Firefox</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Above browsers support push notifications in both <code class=\"language-text\">desktop</code> &#x26; <code class=\"language-text\">mobile</code>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"conclusion\" style=\"position:relative;\">Conclusion<a href=\"#conclusion\" aria-label=\"conclusion permalink\" class=\"blog-post-heading-link after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>As a user just like you, I get irritated whenever I see the push notification prompt on unwanted times and on every page load.</p>\n<p>So once the user <code class=\"language-text\">blocks</code> the permission, there is no way to ask for permission again unless user clears the site cache. So focus on the user and show permission prompt only when it is <code class=\"language-text\">relevant</code>. Thanks for reading my post. See you in next post :)</p>\n<h4>References &#x26; Articles</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://web-push-book.gauntface.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Web Push Book\n</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://tests.peter.sh/notification-generator/\" target=\"_blank\">Push Notification Generator\n</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://demopwa.in\" target=\"_blank\">Demo PWA</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading my blog post 😁.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"Mar 20, 2017","updated":null,"slug":"/blog/2017/best-practices-for-push-notifications","title":"Best Practices for Push Notifications","description":null,"relative":null},"fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2017/best-practices-for-push-notifications"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3633477710"]}